=== 训练 ===
24名（一说26名<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5265938.ece|title=City fears five terrorists are missing| location=London|work=The Times|date=2008-12-02|accessdate=2010-04-23|first=Rhys|last=Blakely}}{{subscription required|date=November 2012}}</ref>）学员在[[克什米尔|克什米尔]]的穆扎法拉巴德的营地中接受海上战争的恐怖训练，据报道，一部分训练在曼格拉大坝进行<ref>{{cite news|last=Rahman|first=Maseeh|author2=Jones, Sam|title=Rumours abound as inquiry begins its search for truth|work=The Guardian|date=2008-12-01|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/dec/01/mumbai-terror-attacks-india-pakistan1|accessdate=2008-12-01|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202011506/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/dec/01/mumbai-terror-attacks-india-pakistan1|archivedate=2008-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

据印度和美国媒体报道，学员主要接受以下几个阶段的训练：

* 心理操控：灌输[[伊斯兰主义|伊斯兰主义]]思想，包括所谓的穆斯林在印度<ref name="hindu.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/12/02/stories/2008120259961000.htm|title=A journey into the Lashkar, Praveen Swami, The Hindu, 02 December 2008|location=Chennai|date=2008-12-02|accessdate=2014-03-29|archive-date=2008-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205005025/http://www.hindu.com/2008/12/02/stories/2008120259961000.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[车臣|车臣]]、[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]等地遭受暴行的图像。
* 基本战斗：虔诚军的基本战斗训练及恐怖袭击策划课程'''Daura Aam'''。
* 高级训练：在曼塞拉附近进行称为'''Daura Khaas'''<ref name="hindu.com"/>的高级训练课程，根据美国国防部一位不愿意透漏姓名的官员所述，课程包括在巴军退伍军人监督下展开的进阶武器和爆炸物培训<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?_r=2&hp|title=New York Times, Quoting a former US defence official|work=The New York Times|first1=Eric|last1=Schmitt|first2=Somini|last2=Sengupta|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2010-04-23|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925064047/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?_r=2&hp|dead-url=no}}</ref>、求生特训和进一步洗脑。
* 突击训练：最后对所选拔的专业突击队开展战术训练，而敢死队则接受为航海前往孟买所做的训练{{Citation needed|date=February 2014}}。

执行孟买任务的10名学员被精心挑选<ref>{{cite news|last=Lakshmi|first=Rama|title=Details Emerge From Sole Arrested Gunman|work=The Washington Post|date=2008-12-03|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/12/02/AR2008120202968_2.html|accessdate=2008-12-03|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403075543/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/12/02/AR2008120202968_2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他们亦接受游泳和帆船的培训，及在虔诚军指挥官的监督下熟习使用高端武器和爆炸物。有媒体援引美国一名不愿透露姓名的前国防部官员，美国的情报机构已认定巴基斯坦的陆军和[[三军情报局|三军情报局]]前任官员积极主动地协助了训练<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?hp|title=Ex-U.S. Official Cites Pakistani Training for India Attackers|date=2008-12-03|accessdate=2008-12-04|work=The New York Times|first1=Eric|last1=Schmitt|first2=Somini|last2=Sengupta|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081206013051/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?hp|archivedate=2008-12-06|deadurl=no}}</ref> ，还给予虔诚军四个袭击目标的建筑设计图。

