=== 贾特拉帕蒂·希瓦吉火車站 ===
[[File:2008_Mumbai_terror_attack_VT_bullet_mark.jpg|缩略图]]
袭击于晚上9:30开始，[[穆罕默德·阿吉马·卡萨布|穆罕默德·阿吉马·卡萨布]]與可汗兩人进入[[贾特拉帕蒂·希瓦吉火車站|贾特拉帕蒂·希瓦吉火車站]]大厅使用[[AK-47步枪|AK-47步枪]]肆意开枪射击<ref name=recalls/> <ref name="recalls">{{Cite news|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/top_story_detail.asp?Id=22785|title=Photographer recalls Mumbai attacks|work=[[The_News_International|The News International]]|date=2009-06-16|accessdate=2009-06-17|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hg3Sz06d?url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/top_story_detail.asp?Id=22785|archivedate=2009-06-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>，58人死，104人伤，10:45结束袭击。<ref name="CCTV">{{Cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News/PoliticsNation/3-witnesses-identify-Kasab-court-takes-on-record-CCTV-footage/articleshow/4665196.cms|work=The Economic Times|location=India|title=3 witnesses identify Kasab, court takes on record CCTV footage|date=2009-06-17|accessdate=2009-06-17|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5hg3SZxC0?url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News/PoliticsNation/3-witnesses-identify-Kasab-court-takes-on-record-CCTV-footage/articleshow/4665196.cms|archivedate=2009-06-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>安全部队及紧急救援随后抵达。两名枪手见状旋即逃离现场，沿途向行人和警察开枪，有8名警察被杀。枪手經過一间派出所，里面的警察自知敵不過對方火力而不敢与枪手硬碰硬，選擇关灯和鎖上大门自保。

随后，枪手到達卡玛医院，打算殺死那裡的人，但医院的工作人员将所有病房锁上，使枪手没能得逞。由警察局长汉蒙·卡卡瑞带领的孟买反恐队在火车站搜捕枪手卡萨布和可汗不果，離開火車站繼續搜捕，与枪手在医院旁的车道上交火。卡卡瑞及其他三名警察被杀，唯一的幸存者，警察阿伦·贾达夫受重伤。枪手驾驶警车逃逸，後來棄下警車改用另一輛客车。途中，他们遇到一个在贾达夫无线电求救后警方所设置的路障，双方爆发枪战，可汗被击毙，卡萨布受伤後裝死。只有警棍的員警翁伯（Tukaram Omble）衝向車上被卡萨布開五槍殺害，但翁伯死前緊抓卡萨布的武器讓其他員警得以生擒犯人。

=== 利奥波德咖啡馆 ===
利奥波德咖啡馆是孟买南部戈拉巴堤道一间著名餐厅，是事件的袭击地点之一。<ref name="timesonline">{{Cite news|title =Defiant Leopold café shows that Mumbai is not afraid|work=The Times |location=UK |date=2008-12-01|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5260641.ece|accessdate=2009-03-19 | first1=Rhys | last1=Blakely | first2=Jeremy | last2=Page}}</ref> 两名枪手于11月26日晚在该餐厅开火，至少10人遇害，其中包括外籍人士。

=== 出租车炸弹袭击 ===
定时炸弹引发两起出租车爆炸事件。第一起爆炸于晚上10:40分发生在维列·伊佩尔勒，车上的司机及一名乘客遇害。第二起爆炸于晚上10:20到10:25间发生在旺地崩德，车上包括司机在内的三人当场身亡，15人受伤。<ref name="Tracing the terror route">{{Cite news|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/Tracing-the-terror-route/396335|title=Tracing the terror route|work=The Indian Express|location=India|date=2008-12-10|accessdate=2008-12-09|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7IVRztz?url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/Tracing-the-terror-route/396335|archivedate=2009-05-28|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Mumbai attack: Timeline of how the terror unfolded|url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/top-stories/2008/11/27/mumbai-attack-timeline-of-how-the-terror-unfolded-115875-20929121/|work=Daily Mirror|location=UK|date=2008-11-27|accessdate=2009-05-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7IVr0yz?url=http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/top-stories/2008/11/27/mumbai-attack-timeline-of-how-the-terror-unfolded-115875-20929121/|archivedate=2009-05-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 泰姬玛哈酒店和欧贝罗伊三叉戟 ===
{{main|泰姬玛哈酒店|奥布罗伊酒店}}
泰姬玛哈酒店和欧贝罗伊三叉戟酒店是袭击中的四个针对性地点之二，有六起爆炸发生在泰姬酒店——一起在大堂、一起在三叉戟的餐厅、两起在电梯、三起在餐厅。<ref name="IBN-Taj">{{Cite news|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/taj-hotel-burns-2-terrorists-killed/79137-3.html|title=Taj Hotel Burns, 2 Terrorists Killed|date=2008-11-27|accessdate=2008-11-27|publisher=[[CNN_IBN|CNN IBN]]|archive-date=2011-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110824211653/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/taj-hotel-burns-2-terrorists-killed/79137-3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="TTKN News">{{Cite news|url=http://www.ttkn.com/world/terror-attacks-army-stormed-taj-hotel-mumbai-217.html|title=Taj Hotel Attacked|date=2008-11-27|accessdate=2008-11-27|publisher=TTKN News|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090113213148/http://www.ttkn.com/world/terror-attacks-army-stormed-taj-hotel-mumbai-217.html|archive-date=2009-01-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>在泰姬酒店，消防员通过云梯从窗户中救出200名人质。

CNN于2008年11月27日上午报道称，泰姬酒店的人质危机已经解决，并援引[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]警察局长的话，称所有人质均已撤离。<ref name="CNN">{{Cite news|title=Scores killed in Mumbai rampage|publisher=CNN|date=2008-11-26|url=http://www.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/26/india.attacks/index.html|accessdate=2008-11-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202062331/http://www.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/26/india.attacks/index.html|archivedate=2008-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>然而，当天晚些有报道称，两名枪手仍在酒店内胁持人质，其中包括外籍人士。<ref name="CNN-27th">{{Cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/27/india.attacks/index.html|date=2008-11-27|title=Fighting reported at Mumbai Jewish center|author=Andrew Stevens, Mallika Kapur, Phil O'Sullivan, Phillip Turner, Ravi Hiranand, Yasmin Wong and Harmeet Shah Singh|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2008-11-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202132254/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/27/india.attacks/index.html|archivedate=2008-12-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>

在袭击期间，快速行动部队、海军突击队和国家安全卫队突击队将两所酒店包围<ref>{{Cite news | first=Anjana | last=Pasricha | title=Commandos Launch Operations to Clear Luxury Hotels Seized by Gunmen in Mumbai | date=2008-11-27 | publisher=Voice of America | url=http://voanews.com/english/archive/2008-11/2008-11-27-voa9.cfm | work=VOA News | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110717231100/http://voanews.com/english/archive/2008-11/2008-11-27-voa9.cfm | archivedate=2011-07-17 | deadurl=yes | access-date=2009-01-04 }}</ref><ref name="toi_army_storms">{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Army_storms_Mumbais_besieged_five-star_hotels_/articleshow/3762100.cms |title=We want all Mujahideen released: Terrorist inside Oberoi |accessdate=2008-11-27 |date=2008-11-27 |work=The Times of India |location=India |archive-date=2019-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190715025042/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Army_storms_Mumbais_besieged_five-star_hotels_/articleshow/3762100.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，当有报道称枪手可以在酒店内观看电视直播时，酒店的电视信号被切断。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.variety.com/VR1117996604.html |title=Indian journalists in media firestorm |work=Variety |date=2008-11-30 |author=Patrick Frater |accessdate=2008-12-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202024047/http://www.variety.com/VR1117996604.html |archivedate=2008-12-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 29日上午，安全部队对两所酒店突袭，全部枪手被击毙。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/28/india.attacks/index.html|title=Mumbai operation appears nearly over|publisher=CNN|date=2008-11-29|accessdate=2009-02-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308091722/http://edition.cnn.com/2008/WORLD/asiapcf/11/28/india.attacks/index.html|archivedate=2009-03-08|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="cnn-oberoi-end">{{Cite news|url=http://cnnwire.blogs.cnn.com/2008/11/28/oberoi-standoff-ends/|title=Oberoi standoff ends|date=2008-11-28|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2009-03-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723111457/http://cnnwire.blogs.cnn.com/2008/11/28/oberoi-standoff-ends/|archivedate=2011-07-23|deadurl=yes}}</ref>国家安全卫队少校桑德皮普·尼克利希纳恩在营救腿部中弹的突击队员苏尼尔·雅达夫时遇害。共有32名人质在欧贝罗伊酒店遇害。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://in.rediff.com/news/2008/nov/30mumterror-terrorists-had-no-plans-to-blow-up-taj.htm|title=Terrorists had no plan to blow up Taj: NSG DG|publisher=[[Rediff|Rediff]]|accessdate=2009-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622030627/http://in.rediff.com/news/2008/nov/30mumterror-terrorists-had-no-plans-to-blow-up-taj.htm|archive-date=2011-06-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/nsg-commando-recounts-gunfight-with-terrorists/79466-3.html|title=NSG commando recounts gunfight with terrorists|publisher=[[CNN_IBN|CNN IBN]]|accessdate=2009-11-26|archive-date=2014-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140701051607/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/nsg-commando-recounts-gunfight-with-terrorists/79466-3.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5378549.ece|title=A taste of defiance as massacre hotel opens for high tea|work=The Times |location=UK|date=2008-12-22|accessdate=2011-01-08 | first=Rhys | last=Blakely}}</ref>
