lims Condemn Mumbai Attacks, Call for Black Eid |date=2008-12-04 |accessdate=2009-02-21 |series=Outlook News |work=[[Outlook_(magazine)|Outlook]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718090144/http://news.outlookindia.com/item.aspx?642291 |archive-date=2011-07-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。商界也积极响应，改变交通方式，请求增加国防能力<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://news.yahoo.com/s/ap_travel/20081217/ap_tr_ge/as_travel_brief_india_business_travel |title=Mumbai attack dents business travel |author=Erika Kinetz |date=2008-12-17 |accessdate=2009-02-21 |publisher=Yahoo News |archive-date=2008-12-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081231201918/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap_travel/20081217/ap_tr_ge/as_travel_brief_india_business_travel |dead-url=no }}</ref>。事件亦在全国范围内触发大量市民运动，例如{{le|今日印度集团|India Toady}}的“反恐战争”运动。全国民众自发举行守夜活动，用蜡烛和招贴画寄托对死难者的哀思<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=24804&sectionid=30&Itemid=1&issueid=88 |title=Be the change |publisher=India Today Bureau |date=2009-01-09 |accessdate=2009-02-28 |work=[[India_Today|India Today]] |archive-date=2017-10-09 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20171009143224/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。总部在[[德里|德里]]的{{le|国家安全卫队|National Security Guard}}指挥官因花费10小时向三处事发地点出兵而遭到批评<ref name="India Today">{{Cite news |title=Red tape delays NSG by 6 hours |first=Aman |last=Sharma |accessdate=2009-06-15 |date=2008-11-29 |url=http://indiatoday.digitaltoday.in/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=21305&issueid=82 |work=[[India_Today|India Today]] |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7Ih9916?url=http://indiatoday.digitaltoday.in/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=21305&issueid=82 |archivedate=2009-05-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News/PoliticsNation/Why_did_NSG_take_10_hours_to_arrive/articleshow/3775099.cms |date=2008-11-30 |title=Why did NSG take 10 hours to arrive? |accessdate=2009-06-15 |work=The 