国际反应十分广泛，许多国家和国际组织谴责袭击，并向受害的市民表示哀悼。其他国家的名人也谴责了袭击<ref name="resp">{{Cite news |first=Tom |last=Rivers |title=Mumbai Attacks Draw Worldwide Condemnation |date=2008-11-27 |publisher=Voice of America |url=http://voanews.com/english/archive/2008-11/2008-11-27-voa32.cfm |accessdate=2009-01-01 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20090318031207/http://voanews.com/english/archive/2008-11/2008-11-27-voa32.cfm |archivedate=2009-03-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。媒体报道强调[[Twitter|Twitter]]和[[Flickr|Flickr]]等[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]和互联网社交网络工具在传播袭击资讯时发挥了重要作用。此外，许多印度博客也实况文字直播了袭击<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3530640/Mumbai-attacks-Twitter-and-Flickr-used-to-break-news-Bombay-India.html |title=Mumbai attacks: Twitter and Flickr used to break news |date=2008-11-27 |accessdate=2009-02-21 |author=Claudine Beaumont |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090219031027/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3530640/Mumbai-attacks-Twitter-and-Flickr-used-to-break-news-Bombay-India.html |archivedate=2009-02-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。网络记者借助[[Google地图|Google地图]]建立了袭击地图<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/11/26/tracking-the-mumbai-attacks/?pagemode=print |title=Tracking the Mumbai Attacks |author=Robert Mackey |work=The New York Times |date=2008-11-26 |accessdate=2009-02-28 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626195304/https://thelede.blogs.nytimes.com/2008/11/26/tracking-the-mumbai-attacks/?pagemode=print |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://maps.google.com/maps/ms?ie=UTF8&hl=en&msa=0&ll=18.922445,72.832242&spn=0.007054,0.007864&z=17&msid=105055855763538009401.00045c9d8b16af3ad1008 |publisher=Google Maps |date=2008-11-26 |title=Map of Mumbai attacks |deadurl=no |accessdate=2013-02-06 |archive-date=2014-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140713102537/https://maps.google.com/maps/ms?ie=UTF8&hl=en&msa=0&ll=18.922445,72.832242&spn=0.007054,0.007864&z=17&msid=105055855763538009401.00045c9d8b16af3ad1008 }}</ref>。2009年7月，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》形容事件“可能是纪录最完善的恐怖袭击”<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/21/world/asia/21india.html |title=Suspect Stirs Mumbai Court by Confessing |last=Polgreen |first=Lydia |author2=Vikas Bajaj |date=2009-07-20 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2009-07-21 |archive-date=2019-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717070909/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/21/world/asia/21india.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2010年11月，受害美国人的家属在纽约布鲁克林起诉[[巴基斯坦三军情报局|三军情报局]]中将{{le|艾哈迈德·舒贾·帕夏|Ahmad Shuja Pasha}}在孟买袭击案中是共犯。2011年9月22日，美国驻阿富汗大使馆遭袭击，引发事件的巴基斯坦人手机通话录音和孟买袭击案中的如出一辙<ref name="suit"/>。

== 归因 ==
孟买恐怖袭击在巴基斯坦境内的[[虔诚军|虔诚军]]武装分子策划，有十名年轻的武装男子被送至孟买，通过手机和[[IP电话|IP电话]]与[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]官方进行联络。<ref name="NYT-2008-12-03">{{Cite news |last=Schmitt |first=Eric |author2=Somini Sengupta, Jane Perlez |title=US and India See Link to Militants in Pakistan |work=The New York Times |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/03/world/asia/03mumbai.html?bl&ex=1228453200&en=a32b625bf9928825&ei=5087%0A |accessdate=2008-12-03 |date=2008-12-03 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701062210/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/03/world/asia/03mumbai.html?bl&ex=1228453200&en=a32b625bf9928825&ei=5087%0A |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="NYTdeepties">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/27/world/asia/27pstan.html?pagewanted=print|title=Terror Ties Run Deep in Pakistan, Mumbai Case Shows|newspaper=The New York Times|first=Jane|last=Perlez|first2=Salman|last2=Masood|date=2009-07-27|page=A4|accessdate=2014-03-23|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110131332/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/07/27/world/asia/27pstan.html?pagewanted=print|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ISIlink">{{Cite news |first=Eric |last=Schmitt |last2=Sengupta |first2=Somini |title=Ex-US Official Cites Pakistani Training for India Attackers |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?hp=&pagewanted=print |newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2008-12-04 |accessdate=2008-12-03 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113131420/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/04/world/asia/04india.html?hp=&pagewanted=print |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2009年7月，巴基斯坦当局证实恐怖袭击是由[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]和[[特达|特达]]的虔诚军策划并提供援助的。<ref>{{Cite news| last = Hussain| first = Zahid| title = Islamabad Tells of Plot by Lashkar| place = Islamabad| work = The Wall Street Journal| date = 2009-07-28| url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124872197786784603.html?mod=googlenews_wsj| accessdate = 2009-07-28| archive-date = 2013-05-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130511024541/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB124872197786784603.html?mod=googlenews_wsj| dead-url = no}}</ref> 2009年11月，巴基斯坦当局证实曾有七名男子在袭击前被逮捕。
<ref name="abc20091125">{{Cite news| last = Schifrin| first = Nick| title = Mumbai terror attacks: 7 Pakistanis charged| publisher = [[ABC_News|ABC News]]| date = 2009-11-25| url = http://abcnews.go.com/International/mumbai-terror-attacks-pakistanis-charged/story?id=9176592| accessdate = 2009-12-01| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091127091951/http://abcnews.go.com/International/mumbai-terror-attacks-pakistanis-charged/story?id=9176592| archivedate = 2009-11-27| deadurl = no}}</ref>

孟买警方起初确定37名嫌疑人，包括两名涉嫌参与密谋的的军官，除了他们以外，其他嫌疑人只能通过巴基斯坦别名来辨认身份。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5806381.ece |title=Pakistani Army colonel 'was involved' in Mumbai terror attacks |accessdate=2009-02-26 |author=Rhys Blakely |work=The Times |location=London |date=2009-02-26 |archive-date=2011-08-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814030052/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5806381.ece |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2009年10月，另外两名嫌疑人在美国被捕，他们涉嫌策划孟买恐怖袭击。其中一名叫大卫·黑德利的巴基斯坦裔美国人曾在袭击前多次前往孟买，为凶手搜集影片和GPS资料。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/who-are-david-headley-tahawwur-rana/105433-3.html|title=Who are David Headley, Tahawwur Rana?|date=2009-11-17|publisher=[[CNN_IBN|CNN IBN]]|accessdate=2009-11-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091121085401/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/who-are-david-headley-tahawwur-rana/105433-3.html|archivedate=2009-11-21|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Headley-link-traced-to-Pak-2-LeT-men-arrested/articleshow/5205152.cms|title=Headley link traced to Pak, 2 LeT men arrested|date=2009-11-07|work=The Times of India|location=India|accessdate=2009-11-21|first1=Vishwa|last1=Mohan|archive-date=2019-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190716145353/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Headley-link-traced-to-Pak-2-LeT-men-arrested/articleshow/5205152.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2011年4月，美国向涉嫌参与袭击的四名巴基斯坦男子发出逮捕令，他们被认为是虔诚军成员，负责帮助策划和培训袭击者。<ref>[[美联社|美联社]], "Four more men charged in Mumbai attack", ''[[日本时报|日本时报]]'', 2011年4月27, 第四版.</ref>

=== 与巴方的交涉 ===
巴基斯坦起初否认要为事件负责，而归咎于在孟加拉国和印度的阴谋者。<ref name="Dawn_Bdeshlink">{{Cite news|authors=Baqir Sajjad Syed and Mohammad Asghar|title=Investigators see Bangladesh link in Mumbai terror attacks|work=[[Dawn_(newspaper)|Dawn]]|date=2009-02-09|url=http://www.dawn.com/2009/02/05/top2.htm|accessdate=2009-02-10|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7IUEUW8?url=http://www.dawn.com/2009/02/05/top2.htm|archivedate=2009-05-28|deadurl=no}}</ref> 印度为此予以反驳<ref name="hindu020909">{{Cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/000200902092232.htm|title=Chidambaram asserts 26/11 originated from Pak soil|work=The Hindu|date=2009-02-09|accessdate=2009-02-21|location=Chennai, India|archive-date=2012-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121105141847/http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/000200902092232.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，声称相关的证据已在第一时间搜集<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dawn.com/2009/02/16/top5.htm |title=Samjhota, Mumbai attacks linked, says Qureshi |accessdate=2009-02-16 |author=Shakeel Ahmad |work=[[Dawn_(newspaper)|Dawn]] |date=2009-02-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090219175006/http://dawn.com/2009/02/16/top5.htm |archivedate=2009-02-19 |deadurl=no }}</ref>
。最终在2009年1月7日，当局承认[[穆罕默德·阿吉马·卡萨布|卡萨布]]为巴基斯坦人<ref name="TIME08JAN2009">{{Cite news| url= http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1870267,00.html| title= Pakistan Continues to Resist India Pressure on Mumbai| work= Time| date= 2009-01-08| accessdate= 2009-01-08| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090114080611/http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1870267,00.html| archivedate= 2009-01-14| deadurl= no}}</ref><ref name="PakAdmitsNYT">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/08/world/asia/08pstan.html|title=Gunman in Mumbai Siege a Pakistani, Official Says|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|author=Richard A. Oppel and Salman Masood|date=2009-01-07|accessdate=2009-02-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301130213/http://nytimes.com/2009/01/08/world/asia/08pstan.html|archivedate=2009-03-01|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.dawn.net/wps/wcm/connect/Dawn%20Content%20Library/dawn/news/pakistan/surviving-gunmans-identity-established-as-pakistani-ss |title=Surviving gunman’s identity established as Pakistani |author=Mubashir Zaidi |work=[[Dawn_(newspaper)|Dawn]] |date=2009-01-07 |accessdate=2009-01-07 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7IXS0KL?url=http://www.dawn.net/wps/wcm/connect/Dawn%20Content%20Library/dawn/news/pakistan/surviving-gunmans-identity-established-as-pakistani-ss |archivedate=2009-05-28 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，他还策划了另外三起针对巴基斯坦人的案件。

印度向巴基斯坦及其他国家提供了审讯记录、武器和袭击过程中通话录音等证据<ref name="DossierNYT">{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/01/07/world/asia/07india.html |title=Dossier From India Gives New Details of Mumbai Attacks |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2009-02-14 |date=2009-01-06 |author=Somini Sengupta |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221221025/http://nytimes.com/2009/01/07/world/asia/07india.html |archivedate=2009-02-21 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.deccanherald.com/CONTENT/Jan42009/scroll20090104110538.asp?section=frontpagenews|title=PC heads for US with 26/11 proof|author=Anirban Bhaumik|work=Deccan Herald |location=India|date=2009-01-04|accessdate=2009-02-21}}{{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>，另据印度官员透露，此次袭击极为复杂使得疑犯必须得到政府部门的官方支持，这一猜测被巴基斯坦否认<ref name="ISIlink" /><ref name="PakAdmitsNYT" />。

迫于美国和联合国的压力，巴基斯坦逮捕数名虔诚军成员，将组织者软禁在家并在几天后被释放<ref name="bloomberg20090128">{{Cite news| title = Pakistan’s Partial Crackdown Lets Imams Preach Jihad| url = http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601080&sid=aF44YOpTiIJk| last = Rupert| first = James| date = 2009-01-28| accessdate = 2009-12-06| work = Bloomberg| archive-date = 2019-08-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190822003735/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=09137a80-c475-11e9-8553-25cd0c7599fa&url=L2FwcHMvbmV3cz9waWQ9MjA2MDEwODAmc2lkPWFGNDRZT3BUaUlKaw==| dead-url = no}}</ref>。时隔一年，孟买警方抱怨巴基斯坦当局不配合案件的侦查<ref name="hindu20091123">{{Cite news | url = http://www.hindu.com/2009/11/27/stories/2009112756271000.htm | title = Missing evidence mars Mumbai massacre probe | author = Praveen Swami | work = The Hindu | date = 2009-11-23 | location = Chennai, India | accessdate = 15 July 2011 <!--DASHBot--> | archive-date = 2012-11-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105141857/http://www.hindu.com/2009/11/27/stories/2009112756271000.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。与此同时，巴基斯坦记者透露，当地安全机构阻止他们采访卡萨布的家乡的人。<ref name="rsf20091113">{{Cite news | url = http://en.rsf.org/pakistan-two-journalists-held-after-helping-13-11-2009,34979.html | title = Two journalists held after helping media probe Mumbai attacker’s background | publisher = Reporters Without Borders | date = 2009-11-13 | author = Reporters Without Borders | accessdate = 15 July 2011 <!--DASHBot--> | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080609/http://en.rsf.org/pakistan-two-journalists-held-after-helping-13-11-2009,34979.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="hindu20091124">{{Cite news | url = http://beta.thehindu.com/news/national/article53785.ece | title = Kasab’s village remains a no-go area for journalists | author = Nirupama Subramanian | work = The Hindu | date = 2009-11-24 | location = Chennai, India | accessdate = 15 July 2011 <!--DASHBot--> | archive-date = 2009-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091130204126/http://beta.thehindu.com/news/national/article53785.ece | dead-url = no }}</ref>内政部长奇丹·巴拉姆表示，巴基斯坦当局没有共享关于美国怀疑黑德利和拉纳的任何信息，但联邦调查局的侦查已先人一步<ref name="toi20091201">{{Cite news| url = http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/No-information-on-Headley-Rana-from-Pakistan-says-home-minister-Chidambaram/articleshow/5288207.cms| title = No information on Headley, Rana from Pakistan, says Home Minister Chidambaram| date = 2009-12-01| work = The Times of India| location = India| author = PTI| accessdate = 15 July 2011 <!--DASHBot-->| archive-date = 2020-11-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111082305/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/No-information-on-Headley-Rana-from-Pakistan-says-home-minister-Chidambaram/articleshow/5288207.cms| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

印度发表了一份关于审问于2010年10月被释放的{{link-en|大卫·黑德利|David Headley}}的情报<ref name="ap-20101019">{{Cite news|url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20101019/ap_on_re_as/as_india_mumbai_attack|title=Indian gov't: Pakistan spies tied to Mumbai siege|publisher=Yahoo! News|agency=Associated Press|date=2010-10-19|accessdate=2010-10-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101021114840/http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20101019/ap_on_re_as/as_india_mumbai_attack|archivedate=2010-10-21|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，报告声称，巴基斯坦情报机构三军情报局（ISI）为袭击前在孟买的侦查提供资金支持<ref name="fox-20101019">{{Cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2010/10/19/indian-report-pakistan-spies-tied-mumbai-siege/|date=2010-10-19|accessdate=2010-10-20|title=Report: Pakistan Spies Tied to Mumbai Siege|agency=Associated Press|publisher=Fox News Channel|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101122010702/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2010/10/19/indian-report-pakistan-spies-tied-mumbai-siege/|archivedate=2010-11-22|deadurl=no}}</ref> 。据黑德利所述，虔诚军的军事统帅扎基·乌尔·拉赫曼·拉赫维频繁与ISI联系，宣称虔诚军的每一次大行动都在与ISI密切配合中大功告成<ref name="fox-20101019"/>。

=== 事件调查 ===
[[File:Mumbai_attacks_vinu_image01-crop.jpg|缩略图]]
根据调查，袭击者从巴基斯坦[[卡拉奇|卡拉奇]]乘船出发，途径[[阿拉伯海|阿拉伯海]]时胁持了名为"Kuber"的印度拖网渔船，他们杀害船上四名船员后，胁迫船长航行至孟买。在谋杀船长后，袭击者乘坐随船的橡皮艇上岸<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News/PoliticsNation/Slain_navigator_of_Porbandar_trawler_was_imprisoned_in_Pak/articleshow/3777132.cms|title=Slain navigator of Porbandar trawler was imprisoned in Pak|date=2008-09-30|accessdate=2009-02-15|work=The Economic Times|location=India|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5h7IWEIuY?url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/News/PoliticsNation/Slain_navigator_of_Porbandar_trawler_was_imprisoned_in_Pak/articleshow/3777132.cms|archivedate=2009-05-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>。此前，Kuber号船长阿马尔·辛格·索兰奇因在巴基斯坦海域非法捕鱼在当地被囚禁六个月，而袭击者在登上前往孟买的小船前，在虔诚军卡拉奇附近的齐萨巴德的安全屋受训。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/articleshow/3816639.cms|title=Terror boat was almost nabbed off Mumbai|date=2008-12-10|accessdate=2010-05-17|work=The Economic Times|location=India|archive-date=2019-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713132124/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/articleshow/3816639.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>

大卫·黑德利是虔诚军的成员，曾在2002年到2009年间为组织频繁往返于各地。黑德利在组织里接受轻武器和[[反追踪|反追踪]]训练，设立可供内部联系的网络，担任为袭击物色目标的首席侦查员<ref name="nytimes1">''New York Times'', 16 October 2010 "US Had Warnings on Plotter of Mumbai Attack," http://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/17/world/asia/17headley.html?pagewanted=1&_r=1&ref=global-home {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/10/17/world/asia/17headley.html?pagewanted=1&_r=1&ref=global-home |date=20200926095344 }}</ref><ref>Pro Publica, 15 October 2010 "FBI Was Warned Years in Advance of Mumbai Attacker’s Terror Ties," http://www.propublica.org/article/mumbai-plot-fbi-was-warned-years-in-advance {{Wayback|url=http://www.propublica.org/article/mumbai-plot-fbi-was-warned-years-in-advance |date=20201120181432 }}</ref>。根据印度当局审讯黑德利的证词，黑德利涉嫌在2006年现金贿赂ISI官员巴克维尔上校，使到上校特地为袭击提供通信，并监视泰姬玛哈酒店模型从而让枪手得知目标方位。一位美国官员表示，黑德利还帮助ISI招募监视印度军队动态的密探。黑德利也是美国毒品管制局的线人，其妻子曾向美国官员警告称其丈夫参与了虔诚军并密谋袭击，泰姬马哈酒店是目标之一<ref name="nytimes1"/>。

美国官员认为，ISI人员官员曾向虔诚军武装人员提供支持<ref name="suit">New York Times, 17 December 2010 "Top US Spy Leaves Pakistan After His Name Is Revealed," http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/18/world/asia/18pstan.html?hp {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/12/18/world/asia/18pstan.html?hp |date=20201113052940 }}</ref>。

在2012年6月被捕的萨比尤丁安·安萨里（化名阿布·哈姆扎）进一步明确了袭击的密谋。根据安萨里所述，袭击早在2006年被计划，印度青年将为袭击卖命。然而组织藏在[[奥兰加巴德|奥兰加巴德]]用于储存AK-47和[[黑索金|旋风炸药]]的仓库在2006年被发现，导致袭击破产。随后哈姆扎跟着虔诚军首领逃到巴基斯坦，物色用于袭击的巴基斯坦青年。2007年9月，十位袭击者出炉。2008年9月，这些袭击者试图从卡拉奇驶向孟买，由于遭遇波涛汹涌的水域被迫返航，最终在2008年11月进行第二次尝试并成功。大卫·黑德利透露三名巴基斯坦军官策划并实施袭击在审讯安萨里时得到证实<ref>{{cite news| url= http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/26/11-Abu-Jundal-names-same-Pak-army-officers-as-Headley-did/articleshow/14619870.cms| title= 26/11: Abu Jundal names same Pak army officers as Headley did| date= 2012-07-03| accessdate= 2014-03-29| archive-date= 2020-11-16| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201116024853/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/mumbai/26/11-Abu-Jundal-names-same-Pak-army-officers-as-Headley-did/articleshow/14619870.cms| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/26-11-had-been-planned-originally-for-2006-reveals-abu-hamza-236374|title=26/11 had been planned originally for 2006, reveals Abu Hamza|publisher=NDTV|date=2012-06-26|accessdate=2012-06-26|archive-date=2015-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150112143035/http://www.ndtv.com/article/india/26-11-had-been-planned-originally-for-2006-reveals-abu-hamza-236374|dead-url=no}}</ref>。安萨里被捕后，巴基斯坦外交部表示，他们已收到有40名印度人涉及袭击的訊息<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Pakistan-says-Mumbai-attackers-were-helped-by-40-Indians/articleshow/14590556.cms|title=26/11: Pakistan says Mumbai attackers were helped by 40 Indians|work=The Times of India|date=2012-07-02|accessdate=2012-07-02|archive-date=2019-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405140444/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Pakistan-says-Mumbai-attackers-were-helped-by-40-Indians/articleshow/14590556.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 袭击手法 ===
袭击者在袭击几个月前得知可以在安全部队离开时隐藏和出现的一些地点，卡萨布告诉警方，组织得到了孟买居民的帮助<ref name="locals">{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Mumbai_locals_helped_us_terrorist_tells_cops/articleshow/3774106.cms |title=Mumbai locals helped us, terrorist tells cops |work=The Times of India |location=India |date=2008-11-30 |accessdate=2008-11-30 |first1=S Ahmed |last1=Ali |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109010053/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/Mumbai_locals_helped_us_terrorist_tells_cops/articleshow/3774106.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |author=Sheela Bhatt |title=Exclusive: LeT terrorist Ismail arrested in Mumbai |publisher=[[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]] |date=2008-11-27 |url=http://www.rediff.com/news/2008/nov/27mum-lashkar-0operative-ismail-arrested-for-attacks.htm |accessdate=2008-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205113835/http://www.rediff.com/news/2008/nov/27mum-lashkar-0operative-ismail-arrested-for-attacks.htm |archivedate=2008-12-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref> 。攻击者至少使用3张在印度-孟加拉国边境购买的[[SIM卡|SIM卡]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,1864539,00.html|title=Pakistani Involvement in the Mumbai Attacks|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2009-02-21|author=Ishaan Tharoor|work=Time|archive-date=2013-02-04|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130204123539/http://www.time.com/time/printout/0,8816,1864539,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，其中有一张在美国新泽西州购得<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5284594.ece|title=Mumbai gunman says he was paid $1,900 for attack – as new CCTV emerges|author=Rhys Blakely|date=2008-12-04|accessdate=2009-02-21|work=The Times|location=UK|archive-date=2011-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814061458/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/asia/article5284594.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度警方透露曾在2008年2月被捕的虔诚军印度籍密探法希姆·安萨里已为11月的袭击物色好目标<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,24757587-663,00.html|title=Indian 'scouted attack' in Mumbai|date=2008-12-06|accessdate=2009-02-21|work=Herald Sun|location=Australia|archive-date=2008-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081212162731/http://www.news.com.au/heraldsun/story/0,21985,24757587-663,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，随后又逮捕了两名印度籍嫌疑人——来自[[喀什米尔|喀什米尔]]斯利那加的米谢赫达尔·艾哈迈德和[[加尔各答|加尔各答]]人陶西夫·拉赫曼，他们为袭击者提供了分别购于加尔各答和新德里的SIM卡<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2008/12/06/mumbai-arrests.html|title=Two men accused of providing SIM cards to Mumbai attackers|date=2008-12-06|accessdate=2009-02-21|publisher=[[CBC_News|CBC News]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090322012902/http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2008/12/06/mumbai-arrests.html|archivedate=2009-03-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

由[[中国北方工业|中国北方工业]]公司制造的86型手榴弹在袭击中被使用<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.forbes.com/2009/08/13/india-china-relations-population-opinions-columnists-gordon-chang.html?partner=relatedstoriesbox |title=India's China Problem – |work=Forbes |date=2009-08-13 |accessdate=2010-12-31 |first=Gordon G. |last=Chang |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126075035/https://www.forbes.com/2009/08/13/india-china-relations-population-opinions-columnists-gordon-chang.html?partner=relatedstoriesbox |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

[[血液检验|血液检验]]表明，袭击者在袭击期间曾服用[[可卡因|可卡因]]和[[D-麦角酸二乙胺|迷幻药]]，以维持体力、保持长达50小时的亢奋，警方更在袭击现场找到了注射器。亦有迹象表明，他们还使用了类固醇<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3540964/Mumbai-attacks-Terrorists-took-cocaine-to-stay-awake-during-assault.html|title=Mumbai attacks Terrorists took cocaine to stay awake during assault|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=London|date=2008-12-03|accessdate=2009-02-21|author=Damien McElroy|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090209010040/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3540964/Mumbai-attacks-Terrorists-took-cocaine-to-stay-awake-during-assault.html|archivedate=2009-02-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>。据幸存的袭击者透露，他们使用[[谷歌地球|谷歌地球]]获悉了袭击的目标建筑物的方位<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3691723/Mumbai-attacks-Indian-suit-against-Google-Earth-over-image-use-by-terrorists.html|title=Mumbai attacks: Indian suit against Google Earth over image use by terrorists|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=London|date=2008-12-09|author=Rahul Bedi|accessdate=2009-02-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090211122758/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3691723/Mumbai-attacks-Indian-suit-against-Google-Earth-over-image-use-by-terrorists.html|archivedate=2009-02-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

十名枪手，九名被击毙，仅有一名被抓获<ref name="NYT_NOV29">{{Cite news |work=The New York Times |date=2008-11-29 |title=India Faces Reckoning as Terror Toll Eclipses 170 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/30/world/asia/30mumbai.html?partner=permalink&exprod=permalink |accessdate=2009-02-21 |author=Somini Sengupta and Keith Bradsher |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116123704/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/11/30/world/asia/30mumbai.html?partner=permalink&exprod=permalink |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bm-saline">{{Cite news |title=Please give me saline |date=2008-11-29 |work=Bangalore Mirror |accessdate=2009-02-21 |location=India |author=Rakesh Prakash |url=http://www.bangaloremirror.com/index.aspx?page=article&sectid=1&contentid=2008112920081129095627277cedee9e0&sectxslt= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090302112856/http://www.bangaloremirror.com/index.aspx?page=article&sectid=1&contentid=2008112920081129095627277cedee9e0&sectxslt= |archivedate=2009-03-02 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。据目击者报告，袭击者多二十岁出头，身穿黑色T桖和牛仔裤，始终面带微笑，看起来对射杀平民津津乐道<ref name="cool">{{Cite news |last=Ramesh |first=Randeep |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/28/mumbai-terror-attacks-india |title=They were in no hurry. Cool and composed, they killed and killed |work=The Guardian |location=UK |date=2008-11-28 |accessdate=2008-11-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201071600/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/28/mumbai-terror-attacks-india |archivedate=2008-12-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

最初有袭击者为英国人的报道<ref name="numbers">{{Cite news |last=Balakrishnan |first=Angela |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/28/british-terrorists-mumbai |title=Claims emerge of British terrorists in Mumbai |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2008-11-28 |accessdate=2008-11-29 |archive-date=2013-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130506063940/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2008/nov/28/british-terrorists-mumbai |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="ASSOCIATED PRESS-27th">{{Cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/new-claims-of-britons-amongst-mumbai-gunmen-1039452.html|title=Arrested Mumbai gunmen 'of British descent'|author=Tom Morgan|work=The Independent|location=UK|accessdate=2008-11-28|date=2008-11-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201062047/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/new-claims-of-britons-amongst-mumbai-gunmen-1039452.html|archivedate=2008-12-01|deadurl=yes}}</ref>，但印度政府表示没有证据证明这一点<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3533837/Mumbai-attack-Government-has-no-evidence-of-British-involvement.html|title=Mumbai attack: Government 'has no evidence of British involvement'|date=2008-11-28|accessdate=2009-02-28|author=Jon Swaine|work=The Daily Telegraph|location=London|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202210536/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3533837/Mumbai-attack-Government-has-no-evidence-of-British-involvement.html|archivedate=2009-02-02|deadurl=no}}</ref>。同样，早期报告声称有十二名枪手<ref>{{Cite news| last = McElroy| first = Damien| title = Mumbai attacks: police admit there were more than ten attackers| work = The Daily Telegraph| location = London| date = 2008-12-06| url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3628614/Mumbai-attacks-police-admit-there-were-more-than-ten-attackers.html| accessdate = 2009-08-04| archive-date = 2020-11-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201128102658/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/india/3628614/Mumbai-attacks-police-admit-there-were-more-than-ten-attackers.html| dead-url = no}}</ref>也未经证实<ref name="DossierNYT" />。

12月9日，十名袭击者的身份和籍贯被孟买警方证实，分别为：来自{{link-en|法德科特|Faridkot, Okara|Faridkot}}的阿杰马勒·阿米尔、来自{{link-en|德拉·伊斯·梅尔汗|Dera Ismail Khan}}的{{link-en|阿布·伊斯梅尔·德拉·伊斯·梅尔汗|Abu Ismail Dera Ismail Khan}}、来自[[木尔坦|木尔坦]]的哈菲兹·艾尔沙德和巴布尔·依木兰、来自[[奥卡拉|Okara]]的贾伟德、来自{{link-en|那劳瓦|Narowal}}的韶艾博、来自[[费萨拉巴德|费萨拉巴德]]的纳兹赫、来自阿里沃尔拉的阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼、来自德帕珀的法赫·德乌拉、来自[[西北边境省|西北边境省]]的德拉·伊斯梅尔·汗，其余的则在巴基斯坦[[旁遮普|旁遮普]]省<ref name="NYTFullNames">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/10/world/asia/10mumbai.html|title=Mumbai Attackers Called Part of Larger Band of Recruits|work=The New York Times|author=Jeremy Kahn and Robert F. Worth|date=2008-12-09|accessdate=2009-02-21|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129055241/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/12/10/world/asia/10mumbai.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年4月6日，包括孟买在内的[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]内政部长通知巴大使馆，九名袭击者尸体已于2010年1月在一处秘密地点安葬。在全市的穆斯林神职人员拒绝土葬袭击者后，尸体曾一度安放在孟买医院的太平间<ref>[http://in.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idINSGE6350JE20100406 Bodies of nine Mumbai gunmen buried secretly in Jan] {{Wayback|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/domesticNews/idINSGE6350JE20100406 |date=20210502111453 }}[[Reuters|Reuters]], Tue 6 April 2010 10:26 pm IST</ref>。

=== 逮捕过程 ===
阿吉马·卡萨布是唯一一位被警方活捉的袭击者<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/12/02/stories/2008120259961000.htm|title=A journey into the Lashkar|author=Swami, Praveen|date=2008-12-02|accessdate=2008-12-05|work=The Hindu|location=Chennai, India|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081205005025/http://www.hindu.com/2008/12/02/stories/2008120259961000.htm|archivedate=2008-12-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>，他向孟买警方供述了袭击者的准备工作、路程和活动<ref name="azam">{{Cite news | title = Planned 9/11 at Taj, reveals caught terrorist | url = http://www.zeenews.com/nation/2008-11-29/487150news.html | publisher = [[Zee_TV|Zee News]] | date = 2008-11-29 | accessdate = 2009-02-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081225174923/http://www.zeenews.com/nation/2008-11-29/487150news.html | archive-date = 2008-12-25 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。

2009年2月12日，巴基斯坦内政部长拉赫曼·马利克表示，巴基斯坦籍的贾伟德·伊科巴勒因在西班牙为孟买的袭击者购买[[VoIP|VoIP]]电话，曾协助转移用于袭击的资金而被逮捕<ref name="nd">{{Cite news |url=http://www.ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/mumbaiterrorstrike/Story.aspx?ID=NEWEN20090083331&type=News |title=Part of 26/11 plan made on our land, admits Pakistan |publisher=[[NDTV|NDTV]] |date=2009-02-12 |accessdate=2009-02-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090213155833/http://ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/mumbaiterrorstrike/Story.aspx?ID=NEWEN20090083331&type=News |archivedate=2009-02-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。另有两名叫汗和里亚玆（全名未公布）的男子亦被逮捕<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/12/us-pakistan-india-idUSTRE51B25820090212|title=Pakistan says it arrests Mumbai attack plotters|author=Kamran Haider|agency=Reuters|date=2009-02-12|accessdate=2012-06-26|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/68hEcXrzQ?url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/12/us-pakistan-india-idUSTRE51B25820090212|archivedate=2012-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两名巴基斯坦人在意大利[[布雷西亚|布雷西亚]]（米兰东部）被逮捕，2009年11月21日被指提供袭击的后勤支持，利用虚假身份证向网上账号转移超过200美元<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://beta.thehindu.com/news/international/article52322.ece|title=Italy arrests two for Mumbai attacks|date=2009-11-21|work=The Hindu|location=India|accessdate=2009-11-21|deadurl=yes|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707022551/http://beta.thehindu.com/news/international/article52322.ece|archive-date=2012-07-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Two Pakistanis arrested in connection with Mumbai attacks|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20091121-two-pakistanis-arrested-brescia-connection-with-mumbai-attacks-italy-india|publisher=France 24|accessdate=2011-08-14|date=2009-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110214075728/http://www.france24.com/en/20091121-two-pakistanis-arrested-brescia-connection-with-mumbai-attacks-italy-india|archive-date=2011-02-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。去年的打击过后，[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]向他们发出了[[红色通缉令|红色通缉令]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Pak mum on 26/11 terror duo held in Italy|url=http://www.timesnow.tv/Pak-mum-on-2611-terror-duo-held-in-Italy/articleshow/4332698.cms|work=The Times of India|location=India|accessdate=2011-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105013259/http://www.timesnow.tv/Pak-mum-on-2611-terror-duo-held-in-Italy/articleshow/4332698.cms|archive-date=2013-11-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2009年10月，两名芝加哥人大卫·科尔曼·黑德利和塔哈乌尔·侯赛因·拉纳，因涉嫌参与境外“恐怖主义活动”被联邦调查局逮捕<ref>{{Cite news|title=Mumbai police probe David Headley's links to 26/11 attacks|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report_mumbai-police-probe-david-headley-s-links-to-26-11-attacks_1308973|date=2009-11-08|work=Daily News and Analysis|location=India|accessdate=2009-11-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091116155352/http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report_mumbai-police-probe-david-headley-s-links-to-26-11-attacks_1308973|archivedate=2009-11-16|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="reuters20091208">{{Cite news| title = India Plans to Try Chicago Man For Mumbai Attacks|url = http://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2009/12/08/news/news-us-india-fbi-mumbai.html| agency=Reuters| date = 2009-12-08| accessdate= 15 July 2011 <!--DASHBot-->| work=The New York Times}} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=RjwilmsiBot}}</ref>。黑德利据称是美籍犹太人，被认为与总部设在孟加拉国的伊斯兰激进团体有联系<ref>{{Cite news|title=David Headley posed as Jew in Mumbai|author=Josy Joseph|url=http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report_david-headley-posed-as-jew-in-mumbai_1309057|date=2009-11-09|work=Daily News and Analysis|location=India|accessdate=2009-11-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091112184125/http://www.dnaindia.com/mumbai/report_david-headley-posed-as-jew-in-mumbai_1309057|archivedate=2009-11-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>。2010年3月18日，黑德利承认数十项指控罪名，从而免于受审。

2009年12月，美国联邦调查局指控巴基斯坦军队的少校阿卜杜勒·拉赫曼·赛义德·哈希姆与黑德利共同谋划袭击案<ref>{{Cite news|title=FBI nails Pak Major for Mumbai attacks|newspaper=[[The_Economic_Times|The Economic Times]]|date=2009-12-09|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/FBI-nails-Pak-Major-for-Mumbai-attacks/articleshow/5317076.cms|accessdate=2009-12-09|archive-date=2020-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201119220318/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics/nation/FBI-nails-Pak-Major-for-Mumbai-attacks/articleshow/5317076.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2010年1月15日，[[印度分析与调查局|印度分析与调查局]]特工在一次成功的收网行动中，抓获11月26日袭击案的策划者之一谢赫·阿卜杜勒·瓦加，他是孟加拉伊斯兰圣战运动印度分支的作战部长，印度最高悬赏的嫌犯。特工经由科伦坡、斯里兰卡，把他引渡到印度的[[海德拉巴_(印度)|海德拉巴]]正式被捕<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/hyderabad/26-11-attacks-handler-arrested/Article1-499019.aspx 26/11 attacks handler arrested] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/hyderabad/26-11-attacks-handler-arrested/Article1-499019.aspx |date=20100129053925 }} ''Hindustan Times'', Abhishek Sharan & Ashok Das, Delhi/Hyderabad, 18 January 2010</ref>。

2012年6月25日，新德里警方逮捕了化名阿布·哈姆扎的扎比尤丁·安萨里，他是袭击新德里[[英迪拉·甘地国际机场|英迪拉·甘地国际机场]]的主要犯罪嫌疑人之一。他的落网被吹捧为是自卡萨布被捕后，案件最为显著的进展<ref>{{cite news|title=Key 26/11 conspirator Abu Hamza arrested at IGI airport in Delhi|url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/key-2611-conspirator-abu-hamza-arrested-in-delhi/267741-3.html|accessdate=2012-06-25|newspaper=IBN Live|date=2012-06-25|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407080750/https://www.news18.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。安全部门已经跟了他三年。安萨里是[[虔诚军|虔诚军]]的极端主义者，是10名袭击者的印地文老师，负有2008年孟买袭击案的责任<ref>{{cite news| url= http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Key-Mumbai-terror-attack-handler-arrested-in-Delhi/articleshow/14384313.cms| title= Key Mumbai terror attack handler arrested in Delhi| date= 2012-06-25| work= The Times Of India| accessdate= 2015-04-04| archive-date= 2019-04-19| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190419025559/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Key-Mumbai-terror-attack-handler-arrested-in-Delhi/articleshow/14384313.cms| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name=hindu_key>{{cite news|title=Key 26/11 terrorist arrested|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article3568185.ece?homepage=true|accessdate=2012-06-25|newspaper=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu]]|date=2012-06-25|location=Chennai, India|first=Praveen|last=Swami|archive-date=2020-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407233752/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/Zabiuddin-arrest-opens-doors-for-2611-probe/article12914651.ece?homepage=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>。被捕后，安萨里在印度当局对各位沙特情报官员的请求下，被引渡到印度被捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ibnlive.in.com/news/2611-suspect-abu-jindal-in-delhi-police-net/267804-3.html |title=26/11 suspect Abu Jundal in Delhi Police net – India News – IBNLive |publisher=Ibnlive.in.com |date=2012-06-28 |accessdate=2012-11-07 |archive-date=2014-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703062132/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/2611-suspect-abu-jindal-in-delhi-police-net/267804-3.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。安萨里被捕后，调查显示他在2009年据称在前立法会议员、马哈拉施特拉邦政府首长法乌兹亚·汗的老立法者旅馆房间里呆了一天。但是首长否认他跟安萨里有任何联系。内政部长奇丹巴拉姆断言，安萨里在巴基斯坦有安全屋，出现在控制室中，没有国家的支持无法行动。安萨里的审讯进一步透露，沙基德·米尔和一名巴基斯坦陆军少校大约两个星期前用假名访问了印度，冒充板球观众调查德里和孟买的目标<ref>{{cite news| url= http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Pakistan-used-cricket-diplomacy-to-survey-terror-targets/articleshow/14514152.cms| title= Pakistan used cricket diplomacy to survey terror targets| date= 2012-06-30| work= The Times Of India| accessdate= 2015-04-04| archive-date= 2019-04-20| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190420181410/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Pakistan-used-cricket-diplomacy-to-survey-terror-targets/articleshow/14514152.cms| dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/NewDelhi/Jundal-had-a-very-safe-haven-in-Pakistan-Chidambaram/Article1-880833.aspx| title= Jundal had a very safe haven in Pakistan: Chidambaram| date= 2012-06-29| access-date= 2012-06-29| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120630092816/http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/NewDelhi/Jundal-had-a-very-safe-haven-in-Pakistan-Chidambaram/Article1-880833.aspx| archive-date= 2012-06-30| dead-url= yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url= http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Maharashtra/Maharashtra-minister-denies-links-with-Jundal-says-ready-for-probe/Article1-878883.aspx| title= Maharashtra minister denies links with Jundal, says ready for probe| date= 2012-06-26| access-date= 2012-06-26| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120626225200/http://www.hindustantimes.com/India-news/Maharashtra/Maharashtra-minister-denies-links-with-Jundal-says-ready-for-probe/Article1-878883.aspx| archive-date= 2012-06-26| dead-url= yes}}</ref>。

== 審訊 ==
卡萨布的审讯因法律问题推迟，印度许多律师不愿意代表他出庭。孟买律师协会（{{lang|en|Mumbai Bar Association}}）通过决定宣告其成员均不代表卡萨布。然而，印度司法部长表示为了审判公正，卡萨布需要律师。最终，卡萨布的律师被找到，但因利益冲突遭更换。2009年2月25日，印度调查人员提交多达11000页的{{le|诉状|chargesheet}}，正式起诉卡萨布犯有谋杀、串谋并发动针对印度的战争等罪名。

2009年5月6日，卡萨布的审讯开始。最初他请求无罪释放，但后来于2009年7月20日承认犯罪。他就袭击案道歉，表示就他犯下的罪行，值得判他死罪，后来又撤回这些言论，声称警方为了迫使他认罪，对他严刑拷打，他在沙滩上漫步时被逮捕。法庭接受了他的上诉，但由于他的认罪书支支吾吾，法官不予撤销86项罪名中的众多项，审判仍需继续。

2010年5月3日，卡萨布的86项指控全部定罪。据发现，他直接谋害七人，在三天的恐怖围攻中故意杀害164人，挑起反对印度的战争，引起恐慌，蓄意杀害两名高级警官。5月6日，他被判处绞刑<ref name="26/11 Kasab held guilty by trial court, 2 Indians walk free">{{Cite news |title=26/11: Kasab guilty; Ansari, Sabauddin Shaikh acquitted |work=The Times of India |location=India |date=2010-05-03 |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Kasab-guilty-Ansari-Sabauddin-Shaikh-acquitted/articleshow/5885540.cms |accessdate=2010-05-04 |archive-date=2019-06-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190626195302/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Kasab-guilty-Ansari-Sabauddin-Shaikh-acquitted/articleshow/5885540.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8664179.stm |title=Mumbai gunman sentenced to death |date=2010-05-06 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2011-07-15 |archive-date=2010-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100508141053/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/8664179.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Mumbai gunman convicted of murder over terror attacks |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2010-05-03 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2010/may/03/mumbai-gunman-4-murder |accessdate=2010-05-03 |first=Gethin |last=Chamberlain |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506073534/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2010/may/03/mumbai-gunman-convicted-murder |archivedate=2010-05-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=26/11 Kasab held guilty 2 Indians walk free |work=The Times of India |date=2010-05-03 |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Kasab-held-guilty-2-Indians-walk-free/articleshow/5887615.cms |accessdate=2010-05-04 |first1=Swati |last1=Deshpande |archive-date=2019-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190405044036/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/26/11-Kasab-held-guilty-2-Indians-walk-free/articleshow/5887615.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而，他就他的刑罚向高级法院上诉。2011年2月21日，孟买高级法院维持卡萨布的死刑，撤回他的上诉<ref name="With HC order, Kasab one step closer to gallows">{{Cite news |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/With-HC-order-Kasab-one-step-closer-to-gallows/articleshow/7543562.cms |title=With HC order, Kasab one step closer to gallows |accessdate=2011-02-22 |work=The Times of India |location=India |date=2011-02-22 |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414074736/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/With-HC-order-Kasab-one-step-closer-to-gallows/articleshow/7543562.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年8月29日，印度最高法院维持了卡萨布的死刑。法庭认为：“除了判处死刑，我们不会留有余地。卡萨布犯下的各类罪行是向印度政府挑起战争<ref name="AFP supreme court">{{cite news |url=http://dawn.com//08/29/verdict-due-on-kasabs-appeal/ |title=Indian Supreme Court upholds death penalty for Kasab |work=Dawn |agency=Agence France-Presse |date=2012-08-29 |accessdate=2012-08-29 }}{{Dead link|date=2018年7月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。”经过为期10个星期的上诉听证，裁决由法官阿夫塔卜·阿拉姆（{{lang|en|Aftab Alam}}）领导的二人最高法院专责小组决定生效。专责小组否认卡萨布没有得到自由公正审判的说法<ref name="Businessweek ruling">{{cite web |url=http://www.businessweek.com/news/2012-08-29/death-sentence-for-mumbai-gunman-upheld-by-india-s-supreme-court |title=Death Sentence for Mumbai Gunman Upheld by India’s Supreme Court |publisher=Bloomberg Businessweek |date=2012-08-29 |accessdate=2012-08-29 |author=Patnaik, Pratap |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130721193410/http://www.businessweek.com/news/2012-08-29/death-sentence-for-mumbai-gunman-upheld-by-india-s-supreme-court |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

卡萨布向印度总统提交了请求恕罪信，但于11月5日遭驳回。2012年11月21日早上7点30分，卡萨布在[[浦那|浦那]]耶尔沃达（{{lang|en|Yerwada}}）绞死，行动代号“X”。[[伊斯兰堡|伊斯兰堡]]的印度特遣团以书信通知巴基斯坦政府卡萨布的绞刑，巴方拒收信件，用传真寄回。卡萨布在巴基斯坦的家人派信使递交他遭绞刑的新闻<ref>{{Cite news |title=Ajmal Kasab hanged at Yerwada Jail in Pune at 7:30 am |work=The Times of India |accessdate=2012-11-21 |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Ajmal-Kasab-hanged-at-Yerwada-Jail-in-Pune-at-730am/articleshow/17303820.cms? |date=2012-11-21 |archive-date=2020-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204135334/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/Ajmal-Kasab-hanged-at-Yerwada-Jail-in-Pune-at-730am/articleshow/17303820.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

